        "headline": "Severe Thunderstorm Watch issued June 7 at 10:21PM CDT until June 8 at 1:00AM CDT by NWS Bismarck ND",
        "description": "SEVERE THUNDERSTORM WATCH 285, PREVIOUSLY IN EFFECT UNTIL 11 PM\nCDT /10 PM MDT/ THIS EVENING, IS NOW IN EFFECT UNTIL 1 AM CDT\n/MIDNIGHT MDT/ MONDAY FOR THE FOLLOWING AREAS\n\nIN NORTH DAKOTA THIS WATCH INCLUDES 20 COUNTIES\n\nIN NORTH CENTRAL NORTH DAKOTA\n\nBOTTINEAU             MCHENRY               PIERCE\nRENVILLE              ROLETTE               WARD\n\nIN NORTHWEST NORTH DAKOTA\n\nBURKE                 MOUNTRAIL\n\nIN SOUTH CENTRAL NORTH DAKOTA\n\nBURLEIGH              GRANT                 MCLEAN\nMERCER                MORTON                OLIVER\nSHERIDAN              SIOUX\n\nIN SOUTHWEST NORTH DAKOTA\n\nADAMS                 DUNN                  HETTINGER\nSTARK\n\nTHIS INCLUDES THE CITIES OF BEULAH, BISMARCK, BOTTINEAU,\nBOWBELLS, CARSON, CENTER, COLUMBUS, DICKINSON, DRAKE, DUNSEITH,\nELGIN, FORT YATES, GARRISON, GLENBURN, GOODRICH, HALLIDAY, HAZEN,\nHETTINGER, KILLDEER, LIGNITE, MANDAN, MCCLUSKY, MINOT, MOHALL,\nMOTT, NEW ENGLAND, NEW LEIPZIG, NEW TOWN, PARSHALL, PORTAL,\nPOWERS LAKE, ROLETTE, ROLLA, RUGBY, SELFRIDGE, SHELL VALLEY,\nSHERWOOD, SOLEN, ST. JOHN, STANLEY, TOWNER, TURTLE LAKE,\nUNDERWOOD, VELVA, WASHBURN, AND WILTON.",
